# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# LAMMPS Input File: Si Interfacial Thermal Conductance (ITC)
# Method: Direct NEMD via Temperature Gradient (Langevin Thermostats)
# Interface: Sigma 5 Twist Grain Boundary
